208 is another mod16 computed value from your encoder.

1920/800 = 2.4
480/2.4 = 200
If i wanted to use 208 i would use 4 pad lines on top and bottom to maintain the AR.  But that sorta screws up zooming.  I would also apply a 2.307 AR setting.
guess im just a sucker for mod16 lol
